class TradeSpec:
    """Trade specification for a single position produced by the optimizer.

    Attributes
    ----------
    position_id : str
        Position identifier.
    instrument_id : str
        Underlying instrument identifier.
    trade_type : TradeType
        Type of trade (existing, new position, close-out).
    current_quantity : float
        Pre-trade quantity.
    target_quantity : float
        Post-trade quantity.
